Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the â€œLost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.text: Now the ones who took it are waking up as 250-year-old psychopaths with a thirst for blood.
